\sinh (\pi a)=\frac12(e^{\pi a}-e^{-\pi a})
\frac{\cosh(a(\pi-x))}{\sinh (\pi a)} = \sum_{n\in\mathbb Z} \exp(-a|x+2\pi n|), \quad 0\le x\le \pi \tag1
(e^{\pi a}-e^{-\pi a})\sum_{n=0}^\infty \exp(-a(x+2\pi n))=\exp(-ax+ a\pi ) \tag2
(e^{\pi a}-e^{-\pi a})\sum_{n=-\infty}^{-1} \exp(a(x+2\pi n))=-\exp(ax-a\pi) \tag3
